		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="64" y="528" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W04" fontSize="80" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffffff" width="350" height="81" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W04" fontSize="80" color="#ffffff">古岩龙蜥</p>
			</content>
			<filters>
				<DropShadowFilter angle="40" color="#ffe599" distance="16" alpha="0.75" quality="2" blurX="25" blurY="25"/>
			</filters>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="575" y="52" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W04" fontSize="48" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffffff" width="318" height="51" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W04" fontSize="48" color="#ffffff">全技能一图流</p>
			</content>
			<filters>
				<DropShadowFilter angle="40" color="#ffe599" distance="16" alpha="0.75" quality="2" blurX="25" blurY="25"/>
			</filters>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="1288" width="435" height="135" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">出场随机获得火水雷冰的一种，并获得<span color="#ffbfbf">20%</span><span>对应元素的抗性。<br/>盾反：护盾必须能扛住该次攻击，方可触发盾反，盾反成功后古岩龙蜥虚弱5s，全抗下降</span><span color="#ffcdbf">50%</span><span>。若盾反成功，则按如下扣除古岩龙蜥的生命值：<br/>1.若为岩盾或对应元素盾，</span><span color="#ffebbf">扣除15%生命值</span><span color="#d6d6d6">；<br/></span><span>2.若不为对应元素盾或岩盾，</span><span color="#ffebbf">扣除5%生命值</span><span>。<br/>幽谷之庇：</span><span color="#ffe599">40岩</span><span>盾，继承10/3倍生命值。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="64" y="661" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W04" fontSize="32" fontStyle="italic" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffe599" width="448" height="35" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W04" fontSize="32" fontStyle="italic" color="#ffe599">曾与「龙王」摇撼山岳的岩龙</p>
			</content>
			<filters>
				<DropShadowFilter angle="40" color="#ffe599" distance="16" alpha="0.75" quality="2" blurX="25" blurY="25"/>
			</filters>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="60" y="981" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W04" fontSize="32" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffffff" width="280" height="35" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
