		</Group>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="408" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">古岩龙蜥使用右爪挥扫，造成<span color="#ffe599">40%</span><span>伤害；古岩龙蜥使用左爪敲地，后拔扯，敲地和拔扯均造成</span><span color="#ffe599">35%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="423" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">古岩龙蜥先用右爪扫击，造成<span color="#ffe599">40%</span><span>伤害，再用左爪划扫，造成</span><span color="#ffe599">50%</span><span>伤害，最后双爪拍击地面造成</span><span color="#ffe599">62.5%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="703" width="423" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">处于古岩龙蜥身后时，古岩龙蜥使用尾部旋扫一圈，造成<span color="#ffe599">50%</span><span>伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧无效)</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="479" width="439" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">古岩龙蜥凝聚自身元素，朝前方扇形区域扫过，造成对应元素的<span color="#ffffbf">40%,20%,10%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="927" width="442" height="258" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">古岩龙蜥产生的「龙鳞」，不同元素的攻击方式不同：<br/><span color="#ff9999">狱火</span><span>：爆炸造成</span><span color="#ff9999">40%</span><span>伤害，留下一片熔岩持续造成</span><span color="#ff9999">10%</span><span>伤害；<br/></span><span color="#7fbfff">清涟</span><span>：在其附近产生7~8次水喷，每个水喷造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">20%</span><span>伤害；<br/></span><span color="#99ffff">青霜</span><span>：产生三波冰棘，依次造成</span><span color="#99ffff">25%,25%,37.5%</span><span>伤害；<br/></span><span color="#ffacff">紫电</span><span>：产生十字雷，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">25%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="703" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff" width="412" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">古岩龙蜥翘尾扔出5个对应自身元素的「龙鳞」，没有伤害。</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="927" width="422" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">当古岩龙蜥的生命值低于<span color="#ffebbf">20%</span><span>时，古岩龙蜥抖动全身，飞出数十个对应元素的「龙鳞」，没有伤害。<br/></span><span color="#ffebbf">(仅限风来人)</span><span>晶鳞四处可转换其元素属性，顺序为</span><span color="#ff9999">火</span><span color="#7fbfff">水</span><span color="#99ffff">冰</span><span color="#ffacff">雷</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/古岩龙蜥.assets/Image_14.png')" x="596" y="171" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/古岩龙蜥.assets/Image_15.png')" x="576" y="150" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="430" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">离古岩龙蜥较远时，古岩龙蜥深入地下,碰到造成<span color="#ffe599">25%</span><span>伤害，然后冒出捶击地面造成</span><span color="#ffe599">75%</span><span>伤害，并在途经上留下对应元素的「龙鳞」。<br/></span><span color="#ffebbf">(仅限风来人)</span><span>出地后获得</span><span textDecoration="underline">幽谷之庇</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
