		<RichText x="738" y="1311" width="1012" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">古岩龙蜥凝聚自身元素之力，朝地面喷射，造成大范围对应元素的<span color="#ffffbf">100%</span><span>伤害，若角色受护盾庇护则只受到对应元素的</span><span color="#ffffbf">25%</span><span>伤害。<br/>该技能可被</span><span textDecoration="underline">盾反</span><span>。此技能在古岩龙蜥生命值低于</span><span color="#ffebbf">15%</span><span>时不再施放。<br/></span><span color="#ffebbf">(仅限风来人)</span><span>原岩喷吐可转换其元素属性，顺序为</span><span color="#ff9999">火</span><span color="#7fbfff">水</span><span color="#99ffff">冰</span><span color="#ffacff">雷</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
